In county and national politics, Nyandarua Governor Francis Kimemia and Water and Irrigation Cabinet Secretary Sicily Kariuki will be leading the Jubilee brigade while Women Representative Faith Gitau will be leading UDA's. 
A wing by UD will be a big blow to Mr Kimemia, who is a strong supporter of President Uhuru Kenyatta and Jubilee.
If the by-election is held before the BBI referendum, the poll results might be an indicator of where Nyandarua residents lie in terms of the handshake and the BBI. 



